                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
              <div class="icon-image-para">
                <div class="icon-image">
                  <img src="<%= asset_path('icon-11.png') %>" class="img-responsive center-block"/>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-para">
                  <h5>REAL SOFTWARE</h5>
                  <p>This isn't just any software, it processes hundreds of donations and thousands upon thousands of dollars,
                  so in your interview when your potential new boss asks if you have work on a 'real' site you yeah, Yeah!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
              <div class="icon-image-para">
                <div class="icon-image">
                  <img src="<%= asset_path('icon-12.png') %>" class="img-responsive center-block"/>
                </div>
