                  <p>In order to participate in these kinds of large-scale projects, you have to learn to work with other people
                  and at Devschool we teach you toold and workflows to faciliate this to happen.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

